| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1829 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0445b0c3-7d63-592f-845d-74ee59cdd71b"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
